    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "a7330ae0_b5fec053",
        "filename": "scheduler/appengine/engine/invquery.go",
        "patchSetId": 11
      },
      "lineNbr": 455,
      "author": {
        "id": 1141499
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-04-18T23:03:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "my PoV is from avoiding GC allocs and saving on CPU spent on bookkeeping. Hence, both allocs are almost the same.\n\nNow I see that your PoV is avoiding extra RAM usage. I don\u0027t buy this as important because 500*8\u003d4KB alloc is nothing comparing 500 actual invocations. We can allocate 4KB 200 times and still be \u003c1MB.\n\nAnyway, no point thinking more about this.",
      "parentUuid": "73ffc8f5_645c85ea",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 455,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 455,
        "endChar": 26
      },
      "revId": "9d146de55fde090f948129b2651d3cb01dedeec6",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "f9805fd2_aaebad58",
        "filename": "scheduler/appengine/engine/invquery.go",
        "patchSetId": 11
      },
      "lineNbr": 455,
      "author": {
        "id": 1002539
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-04-18T23:09:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "To be precise My PoV is to avoid unnecessary O(PageSize) memory, but not necessarily O(1). I consider PageSize to be \"large\".\n\nIn terms of GC, luci-go/luci-gae frameworks generate astonishing amount of garbage already (bringing up and tearing down complex hierarchy of contexts on each request) and +-10 objects make no difference whatsoever.",
      "parentUuid": "a7330ae0_b5fec053",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 455,
